                          
                          
                            Angular -( localhost:4200 ) - Front End Development

{
    project creation: syntax: ng new projec_name --routing

    project run: syntax: ng serve --open

    Component creation: syntax: ng g c Component_name

    service creation: syntax: ng g s service_name

    Directive creation: syntax: ng g d directive_name

    To take Build - ng build --prod

}

                               Angular Concepts


             1. Component - { html, css, ts}- Root Component - AppComponent

             2. Module - Root Module - AppModule

             3. Data Binding - data shairing  within component 

                3.1 One Way Binding

                    3.1.1 Component to View 

                        3.1.1.1 String Interpolation: syntax - {{expression}}

                        3.1.1.2 Property Binding - syntax: [binding-target]="binding-source"

                    3.1.2 View to Component

                        3.1.2.1 Event Binding - syntax: (event-name)="function call"

                        3.1.2.2 Event Binding using $event- syntax: (event-name)="function ($event)"

                        3.1.1.3 Template reference variable - syntax : #variable_name

                3.2 Two Way Binding - FormsModule import -[(ngModel)]="variable_name"

             4. Angular Routing - to set path for component

             5. Dependency Injection - data shairing  between  components/classes
                In constructor :  syntax -  ( access specifies variable_name:dependent class name)

             6. Angular Services - To store reusable / duplicate code within Angular

             7. ngSubmit - use inside form tag, remove event from button tag and 
                           change type of button as submit


             8. Angular Forms

                8.1 Template driven Forms

                8.2 Model driven Forms

                    8.2.1 Reactive Forms - To add Validations - {Add ReactiveFormsModule in app Module}
                          {Form Group, Form Array , Form Control}

            9. Angular Directive - DOM Manipulation

                9.1 Component Directive 

                9.2 Structural Directive -to add/ remove html tag , preceeded by *

                    9.2.1 ngIf - syntax : *ngIf="condition"

                    9.2.2 ngFor

                    9.2.3 ngSwitch

                9.3 Attribute Directive - to set of style to view

                    9.3.1 In Built - ngClass

                    9.3.2 User defined

            10. local storage - store data permantly in browser

                10.1 setItem - To insert

                10.2 getItem - to get data

                10.3 removeItem 

            11. import HttpClientModule

            12. Asynchronous event - Obeservable- RXJS

                12.1 Resolve state - subscribe()

                12.2 Reject state - catch()

            13. Parent Child Communication

                13.1 Parent to Child - Input decorator

                13.2 Child to Parent - Output decorator

            14. Event Emitter- 

            15. Angular Pipes - 


